summary: It’s going to be interesting to finally see the Starks united as a family face off a common threat as a unit. The idea of Jon’s...
body: It’s going to be interesting to finally see the Starks united as a family face off a common threat as a unit. The idea of Jon’s leadership skills, Sansa’s management abilities, the capabilities that Arya gained as an assassin and Bran’s access to a repertoire of information (which are all things that they all managed to gain through years of suffering and isolation) meshing together is honestly going to be interesting. They are a pack, and we’re finally going to see that, and I can’t wait!
